        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks AG for his essay on geology and Athenian history [see <hi rend="doubleUnderline">5784</hi>].</p> 
            <p>Comments on French rejection of evolution. "How strange that the country of Buffon, Geoffroy and especially Lamarck should now cling to species as immutable creations."</p> 
<p><hi rend="italic">Variation</hi> will soon appear in French.</p> 
        </abstract>
